CIRCUMSTANCES

 

On March 24, 2012, Molly Marie Young was found dead in the apartment of her ex-boyfriend, Richie Minton. The apartment is located at 500 North Westridge Drive in Carbondale IL. It is located behind the Medical Arts Center. The gun used to end her life belonged to Richie Minton and he was present at the time of her death. As of this time (6/11/12) he has been uncooperative with authorities and no arrests have been made. If you have ANY information regarding the death of Molly Marie, please call Illinois State Police at (618) 542-2171. 

 

All information will remain CONFIDENTIAL.

